.DT
stat
Discworld Creator help
stat

.SH Name
.SI 5
stat - gets statistics on an item or person
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
stat <person>
stat <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Stat is used to return information about the state of an object.  Stat works
by calling a function stat() on the object and then printing out the returned
information.  The person may be any object at all.

Stat uses wiz_present to match the objects to get the statistics of.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> stat furball
> stat detritus
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
wiz_presetn
.EP
